itemDescription: Miss Cayman Islands 2011, contestant in Miss World 2011 & Miss Universe 2012

wikipedia_page.main: Miss Universe 2012, the 61st Miss Universe pageant, was held on December 19, 2012 at PH Live at Planet Hollywood Resort & Casino, Las Vegas, Nevada, United States. Leila Lopes of Angola crowned her successor Olivia Culpo of the United States at the end of the event, making the eighth crown for the United States at Miss Universe. 89 contestants competed in this year's pageant, same as the last year. This record was broken in 2017 with 92 contestants, which again was broken in 2018 with 94 contestants.
